    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total beauty! This car has been babied since day one\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it honestly still has that new-car feel. It runs like an absolute dream and is in such incredible shape that you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for something that's been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
