    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather remains supple and scent-free, showing no signs of wear on the bolsters, steering wheel, or touchpoints. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is flawless, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every fluid change and inspection performed by certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. No modifications, no stories\u2014just pure, original excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
