    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly so excited for whoever gets to drive this beauty home. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been incredibly picky about keeping it spotless and garage-kept, so it\u2019s still got that 'new car' magic. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
