      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered lineage, maintained to an exacting standard. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features pristine individual throttle bodies and a flawlessly operating VANOS system, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Underneath, the chassis remains rigid with a factory-spec subframe and a limited-slip differential that provides exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry is stock and tight, preserving the communicative feedback these M-cars are renowned for. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a showroom-fresh aesthetic, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
